OL,3,CMan jailed after stealing castle's
OL,4,C#80,000 candelabra in broad daylight
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced after
OL,7,Fpleading guilty to theft of a
OL,8,Fcandelabra from Cyfarthfa Castle in
OL,9,FMerthyr Tydfil in April.
OL,11,FHenry Tyson Wilsher, 31, from
OL,12,FBagworth, Leicestershire was sentenced
OL,13,Fto 32 months at Teeside Crown Court on
OL,14,FThursday. He pleaded guilty to theft,
OL,15,Freceiving stolen good and criminal
OL,16,Fdamage.
OL,18,FThe candelabra, which dated back to
OL,19,Fthe time when the castle was owned by
OL,20,Fthe Crawshay family, was taken from a
OL,21,Fdisplay at the museum on 8 April.
