OL,3,CMan jailed after stealing castle's
OL,4,C#80,000 candelabra in broad daylight
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police said that, on the
OL,7,Fevening of 24 March, a delivery driver
OL,8,Fhad parked his silver Ford car while
OL,9,Fhe briefly left it to make a delivery,
OL,10,Fbut left the car running with the keys
OL,11,Fstill in the ignition. At some point
OL,12,Fafter the theft of the car, Wilsher
OL,13,Fended up in possession of it.
OL,15,FOn 8 April, Wilsher entered the castle
OL,16,Fduring an event where local primary
OL,17,Fschool children were presenting their
OL,18,Fprojects to judges and guests.
