OL,4,C#80,000 candelabra in broad daylight
OL,6,FHe talked to the receptionist, before
OL,7,Fmaking his way to the Crawshay Room,
OL,8,Fsmashing the glass of a display
OL,9,Fcabinet using a brick and stealing the
OL,10,Fcandelabra, which has a value of
OL,11,Faround #80,000.
OL,13,FMerthyr Tydfil Council leader Brent
OL,14,FCarter previously told ITV Wales of
OL,15,Fthe "frightening" incident: "It was
OL,16,Fawful. There were sixty school
OL,17,Fchildren here from Cyfarthfa Park
OL,18,FPrimary.
