OL,3,CMan jailed after stealing castle's
OL,4,C#80,000 candelabra in broad daylight
OL,6,F"They were here enjoying themselves,
OL,7,Flooking around the museum, and a
OL,8,Fgentleman came in, picked a house
OL,9,Fbrick out of his pocket, and smashed
OL,10,Fthe casing, tore back the glass and
OL,11,Fstole the candelabra."
OL,13,FWilsher then fled in the silver Ford
OL,14,FFiesta. South Wales Police then
OL,15,Flaunched an appeal to try and find him.
OL,17,FSeargent Watts of South Wales Police
OL,18,Fsaid: "This was a brazen theft in
OL,19,Fbroad daylight, that left a group of
OL,20,Fschool children shocked and upset.
